# Launch-path breakpoints for 1.05e (see docs/launch-trace.md).
# Comments and blank lines are stripped by the launcher.
#
# After the file browser appears: A on a .GB to open/launch.
# Do NOT enable $078d here — it fires constantly during SD I/O.
# Add it after $1569 with: breakpoint $078d

breakpoint $145f
breakpoint $1569
breakpoint $5e14
watch $7f36
watch $7fe0
watch $7fc0 $7fc4
continue
